OL,4,CCutting methane gas 'crucial for
OL,5,Cclimate fight'
OL,6, Reducing emissions of methane gas is
OL,7, vital for tackling climate change in
OL,8, the short-term, a major UN report says.
OL,10,FMethane is produced when living things
OL,11,Fdecompose; it's also in natural gas.
OL,13,FIt persists for just a short time in
OL,14,Fthe atmosphere - unlike carbon dioxide
OL,15,F- but methane is a much more potent
OL,16,Fglobal warming gas than CO2.
OL,18,FThe report says "urgent steps" are
OL,19,Fnecessary in order to reduce methane if
OL,20,Fglobal warming is to be kept within a
OL,21,Flimit laid down in the Paris deal.
